Description: A calmer internet — privacy-focused Firefox-based browser
 Zen Browser is a Firefox-based browser redesigned from the ground up
 to bring calm and organization to your browsing. It blocks trackers,
 ads, and unwanted content by default.
 .
 Key features:
  * Split Views — browse two pages side-by-side within a single window
  * Workspaces — organize tabs into separate contexts
  * Sidebar-based tab management with compact mode
  * Boosts — customize any website's look and feel
  * Built-in ad blocker and tracking protection (ETP)
  * Compact mode, Glance, and Zen Mods for a clean experience
 .
 This package repackages the official upstream tarball for Devuan,
 with system NSS/NSPR libraries and dictionary integration.
